underlying_goal: To commit new spec files and an updated PDF related to a paper overhaul.
primary_success: Claude identified new spec files and correctly committed them with a single logical commit message.
brief_summary: The user invoked the /commit skill to save work on a paper overhaul. Claude found two new spec files and an updated PDF. It correctly identified that the spec files represented a single logical change and committed them, then asked the user for guidance on whether to also commit the tracked binary PDF file.
